WEBVTT

00:05.614 --> 00:07.659
June: I THINK
I WOULD LIKE TO TAKE

00:07.746 --> 00:09.009
THE USHANKA HAT SPY CAM.

00:09.096 --> 00:10.271
OH.

00:10.358 --> 00:11.881
IT'S GOOD
FOR THE NEW YORK CHILL.

00:11.968 --> 00:14.014
[ CHUCKLES ]WELL, IN THAT CASE,

00:14.101 --> 00:17.060
MAY I INTEREST YOU
IN THIS NUCLEAR-WINTER LANTERN?

00:17.147 --> 00:18.801
OH!
IT GENERATES
VITAMIN "D."

00:18.888 --> 00:20.629
ALWAYS GOOD
TO BE PREPARED.

00:20.716 --> 00:21.847
I'LL TAKE IT.

00:21.934 --> 00:23.023
THANK YOU SO MUCH.

00:23.110 --> 00:25.242
PLEASE TELL ALL OF BYRON'S
OLD FRIENDS.

00:25.329 --> 00:28.115
I NEED AS MANY BUYERS
FOR MY SLEIGHT-OF-HAND-ME-DOWNS

00:28.202 --> 00:29.464
AS I CAN POSSIBLY GET.

00:29.551 --> 00:30.813
YOU KNOW I WILL.
MWAH!

00:30.900 --> 00:32.119
THANKS, DEAR.

00:32.206 --> 00:33.642
SEND THEM?YES, OF COURSE.

00:33.729 --> 00:34.773
THANK YOU.BYE, JUNE.

00:34.860 --> 00:36.427
BYE, DARLING.SEE YOU AT HOME.

00:36.514 --> 00:38.342
YOU KNOW
SHE DOESN'T ACTUALLY NEED

00:38.429 --> 00:40.083
A RUSSIAN-SURPLUS
SPY-CAM HAT.

00:40.170 --> 00:41.389
SHE'S A WONDERFUL WOMAN.

00:41.476 --> 00:43.956
ARE YOU SURE YOU WANT TO
SELL EVERYTHING, MOZ?

00:44.044 --> 00:47.221
I MEAN, I KNOW HOW MUCH
SOME OF THIS STUFF MEANS TO YOU.

00:47.308 --> 00:49.005
WELL,
CAN WE SELL OURTREASURE?

00:49.092 --> 00:50.833
WE KNOW IT'S FROM
RUSSIAN MUSEUMS.

00:50.920 --> 00:52.530
IT'S NOT TAINTED.
IT'LL SELL QUICK.

00:52.617 --> 00:54.402
WITH THE SUB'S MANIFEST
LOCKED AWAY AT THE D.C. BUREAU?

00:54.489 --> 00:56.012
YOU KNOW WE CAN'T RISK IT.

00:56.099 --> 00:59.450
WELL, THEN, YES, I'M GONNA SELL
ALL OF MYTREASURES.

00:59.537 --> 01:00.582
OH, COME ON.

01:00.669 --> 01:02.018
IS IT REALLY THAT DIRE,
OLIVER TWIST?

01:02.105 --> 01:03.541
OH, IT'S WORSE.

01:03.628 --> 01:05.630
REMEMBER I TOLD YOU
ABOUT MR. JEFFRIES?

01:05.717 --> 01:07.110
YEAH.

01:07.197 --> 01:09.373
YOUR OLD HEADMASTER
FROM THE GROUP HOME IN DETROIT.

01:09.460 --> 01:10.853
YEAH, WELL,
THEY LOST ALL THEIR FUNDING

01:10.940 --> 01:12.028
BECAUSE OF THE ECONOMY
IN DETROIT.

01:12.115 --> 01:13.464
I'M SORRY, MOZ.

01:13.551 --> 01:15.205
I SENT AN ANONYMOUS DONATION
LAST MONTH,

01:15.292 --> 01:17.077
BUT THAT'S NOT GONNA LAST
VERY LONG.

01:17.164 --> 01:19.079
THE ORPHANAGE
IS MR. JEFFRIES' ENTIRE LIFE.

01:19.166 --> 01:20.428
THOSE KIDS NEED HIM.

01:20.515 --> 01:23.431
ALL RIGHT, I WILL SPREAD
THE WORD ABOUT THE SALE...

01:23.518 --> 01:25.433
AND I'LL BUY THE BANANA.

01:25.520 --> 01:27.043
EXCELLENT CHOICE.

01:29.001 --> 01:30.394
[ CHUCKLES ]

01:33.354 --> 01:34.920
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]Peter: GUYS, QUIET DOWN.

01:35.007 --> 01:36.357
QUIET DOWN.
LET'S GET THROUGH THIS.

01:36.444 --> 01:38.010
BLAKE, FOLLOW UP WITH BELLEVUE

01:38.098 --> 01:40.012
ABOUT THOSE FAKE
INSURANCE CARDS.

01:40.100 --> 01:42.276
JONES, STOP TEXTING.[ CELL PHONE THUDS ]

01:42.363 --> 01:44.234
PUT A SMILE ON YOUR FACE --
ANOTHER IBF.

01:44.321 --> 01:45.496
I'M SMILING.

01:45.583 --> 01:47.063
DIANA,
COPYRIGHT INFRINGEMENT.

01:47.150 --> 01:48.717
NOT ANOTHER ONE.WHAT WAS THAT?

01:48.804 --> 01:49.979
YAY, ANOTHER ONE.

01:50.066 --> 01:50.936
THAT'S WHAT I THOUGHT
I HEARD.

01:51.023 --> 01:52.199
NEAL...
HERE.

01:52.286 --> 01:53.374
...HELP DIANA
IF SHE NEEDS IT.

01:53.461 --> 01:55.811
ALL RIGHT,
I SAVED THE BEST FOR LAST.

01:55.898 --> 01:58.553
ORGANIZED CRIME IS ASKING US
TO KEEP AN EYE OUT

01:58.640 --> 02:01.295
FOR ANY FINANCIAL MOVEMENT
FROM THE MOTOR CITY.

02:01.382 --> 02:03.906
APPARENTLY,
THE DETROIT MOB'S IN TOWN.

02:03.993 --> 02:05.560
THIS GUY, FRANK DE LUCA,

02:05.647 --> 02:08.824
HAS BEEN SPOTTED POKING AROUND
OUR LOCAL CRIMINAL HOT SPOTS.

02:08.911 --> 02:12.219
ORGANIZED CRIME THINKS
THAT HE'S LOOKING FOR SOMEBODY.

02:12.306 --> 02:13.916
DO THEY KNOW WHO?

02:14.003 --> 02:17.528
NO, BUT LAST NIGHT,
THIS NUMBERS RUNNER

02:17.615 --> 02:19.400
MET WITH
AN UNFORTUNATE ACCIDENT

02:19.487 --> 02:22.185
AFTER SOMEBODY TRIED
GETTING INFORMATION OUT OF HIM.

02:22.272 --> 02:24.709
O.C. SUSPECTS IT WAS DE LUCA
DOING THE ASKING.

02:24.796 --> 02:26.668
WE GOT AL CAPONE
ON TAX EVASION.

02:26.755 --> 02:29.714
MAYBE THERE'S A FINANCIAL ANGLE
THAT WE CAN PLAY DE LUCA.

02:29.801 --> 02:31.890
THAT'S IT.
MEETING ADJOURNED.

02:31.977 --> 02:33.588
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

02:33.675 --> 02:36.243
SOUNDS LIKE
WE'VE GOT AN EASY DAY.

02:36.330 --> 02:37.983
WE DO.
PLEASE DON'T COMPLICATE IT.

02:38.070 --> 02:40.464
I WOULD NEVER.
CAN I TAKE AN EARLY LUNCH?

02:40.551 --> 02:41.944
SURE.

02:44.990 --> 02:47.297
SOMETHING WRONG, BOSS?

02:47.384 --> 02:49.386
NEAL JUST COMPLICATED
MY DAY.

02:49.473 --> 02:52.607
HAVE ORGANIZED CRIME GET THOSE
FILES ON THE DETROIT MOB.

02:52.694 --> 02:55.000
YOU GOT IT.

03:01.181 --> 03:03.705
OKAY, YOU DEGENERATES,
LISTEN UP.

03:03.792 --> 03:05.968
THERE ARE GREAT
OPPORTUNITIES HERE.

03:06.055 --> 03:08.710
WE'VE GOT ULTRASONIC
STUN-GUN BINOCULARS,

03:08.797 --> 03:12.148
CANE SWORDS, CATTLE PRODS,
MORNING-STAR MACES.

03:12.235 --> 03:13.541
THIS IRON DO ANYTHING?

03:13.628 --> 03:15.325
OH, YOU EVER NEED
A MULTI-DIRECTIONAL MIKE

03:15.412 --> 03:17.719
WITH OPTIONAL TEAR-GAS
DISPENSER VALVE?

03:17.806 --> 03:19.024
NO.

03:19.111 --> 03:20.678
WHO'S THIS LITTLE GUY?

03:20.765 --> 03:23.028
OH, NO, NO, NO.
NO, IT'S NOT FOR SALE.

03:23.115 --> 03:24.900
CAN'T HAVE THAT.
HERE, UH, TRY THIS.

03:24.987 --> 03:26.467
NO, DON'T EAT THIS.
TRUST ME.

03:26.554 --> 03:28.033
MOZ, I NEED TO
TALK TO YOU.

03:28.120 --> 03:29.861
NOT NOW, NEAL.THIS IS IMPORTANT.

03:29.948 --> 03:32.908
DID YOU TALK
TO A NUMBERS RUNNER RECENTLY?

03:32.995 --> 03:34.910
UH, YEAH, EDDIE NINE-BALL.
WHY?

03:34.997 --> 03:36.520
HE'S DEAD, MOZ.

03:36.607 --> 03:40.089
HEY, LISTEN UP,
NEW YORK UNDERWORLD.

03:40.176 --> 03:43.658
I'M FRANK DE LUCA JR.
FROM DETROIT,

03:43.745 --> 03:45.181
AND I'M HERE LOOKING FOR A MAN

03:45.268 --> 03:47.879
WHO'S KNOWN AS
"THE DENTIST OF DETROIT."

03:47.966 --> 03:49.881
[ LIGHT LAUGHTER ]

03:49.968 --> 03:52.232
SO YOU THINK THE DENTIST
IS A MYTH, HUH?

03:52.319 --> 03:55.235
NO ONE MAN COULD
DO EVERYTHING HE'S DONE.

03:55.322 --> 03:59.064
WELL, I'M HERE TO TELL YOU --
THE DENTIST IS REAL,

03:59.151 --> 04:00.501
AND I HAVE
GOOD REASON TO BELIEVE

04:00.588 --> 04:02.067
HE'S RIGHT HERE
IN NEW YORK CITY.

04:02.154 --> 04:06.202
AND SO, SURELY, ONE OF YOU
KNOWS WHO THE DENTIST IS.

04:08.813 --> 04:10.554
OKAY.

04:10.641 --> 04:12.426
PLEASE...

04:12.513 --> 04:14.645
TELL THE DENTIST
THAT I'M MAKING AN APPOINTMENT,

04:14.732 --> 04:17.344
AND IF HE DOESN'T
KEEP IT...

04:20.608 --> 04:22.697
...HE CAN SAY GOOD-BYE
TO HIS FRIEND.

04:33.577 --> 04:35.623
THAT'S MR. JEFFRIES.

04:35.710 --> 04:36.624
WHAT'S GOING ON, MOZ?

04:36.711 --> 04:39.366
NEAL...

04:39.453 --> 04:41.411
I'M THE DENTIST
OF DETROIT.

05:06.044 --> 05:08.351
Peter: THIS EVERYTHING
FROM ORGANIZED CRIME?

05:08.438 --> 05:09.613
INCLUDING A MAP
OF DE LUCA'S

05:09.700 --> 05:11.093
SUSPECTED MOVEMENTS
AROUND THE CITY.

05:11.180 --> 05:12.529
WHAT DO YOU KNOW
ABOUT HIM?

05:12.616 --> 05:14.357
DE LUCA SR.
WAS GUNNED DOWN FIVE MONTHS AGO,

05:14.444 --> 05:16.446
LEAVING HIS SON FRANK TO
TAKE OVER THE FAMILY BUSINESS.

05:16.533 --> 05:19.449
LEO MAZZERA -- DRIVES THE CAR,
SCARES THE PEOPLE.

05:19.536 --> 05:20.755
Jones: WE GOT CAFFREY'S
TRACKING DATA CUED UP.

05:20.842 --> 05:22.017
WHAT DID HE DO NOW?

05:22.104 --> 05:23.975
TOOK AN EARLY LUNCH.

05:24.062 --> 05:25.890
YEAH, REMIND ME TO STAY
ON YOUR GOOD SIDE.

05:25.977 --> 05:28.719
YOU NOTICE HIM PERK UP WHEN
PETER MENTIONED THE DETROIT MOB?

05:28.806 --> 05:30.504
YEAH, BUT WE'VE BEEN TRACKING
CAFFREY FOR SEVEN YEARS.

05:30.591 --> 05:32.810
HE HAS
NO DETROIT TIES.BUT MOZZIE DOES.

05:32.897 --> 05:36.640
JONES, OVERLAY NEAL'S
TRACKING DATA WITH DE LUCA'S.

05:36.727 --> 05:37.946
DE LUCA'S IN RED.

05:38.033 --> 05:39.164
LOOK AT THAT --

05:39.251 --> 05:41.776
NEAL'S MOVEMENTS,
DE LUCA'S MOVEMENTS.

05:41.863 --> 05:44.300
LOOKS LIKE DE LUCA
FOUND WHO HE WAS LOOKING FOR.

05:45.823 --> 05:47.216
Neal: YOU'RE NOT MEETING
DE LUCA.

05:47.303 --> 05:48.783
I'M NOT GOING ALONE.

05:48.870 --> 05:52.047
I'LL HAVE THIS IN THE SKY
TO SCAN THE AREA'S WEAK SPOTS

05:52.134 --> 05:54.354
WHILE YOU GO
TO A HIGHER-GROUND POSITION

05:54.441 --> 05:56.268
WITH YOUR LASER --
MOZ!

05:56.356 --> 05:57.922
ARE YOU ACTIVELY
TRYING TO DIE?

05:58.009 --> 05:59.446
YOU CAN'T TAKE ON
DE LUCA.

05:59.533 --> 06:01.926
NEAL, I'M ON A RESCUE MISSION!
MR. JEFFRIES IS IN TROUBLE.

06:02.013 --> 06:03.754
LET'S KEEP
TALKING THIS THROUGH.

06:03.841 --> 06:05.234
HOW DID DE LUCA FIND YOU?

06:05.321 --> 06:07.192
WELL, HE KNEW I WAS CONNECTED
TO THE GROUP HOME.

06:07.279 --> 06:08.672
HE MUST HAVE TRACKED
MY DONATION.

06:08.759 --> 06:09.847
DID YOU SHORE UP
YOUR ACCOUNT?

06:09.934 --> 06:11.501
I HAD TO TRANSFER THE CASH
IMMEDIATELY --

06:11.588 --> 06:13.024
ONLY HAD TIME
TO DUMMY BACK ONE ACCOUNT,

06:13.111 --> 06:14.112
NOT MY USUAL FOUR.

06:14.199 --> 06:15.113
MM-HMM. THERE YOU GO.

06:15.200 --> 06:17.028
[ BELL RINGS ]

06:17.115 --> 06:18.900
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

06:18.987 --> 06:21.119
IN CASE IT'S DE LUCA.

06:21.206 --> 06:22.643
I'M GONNA STAND
BEHIND YOU.

06:22.730 --> 06:25.341
THAT'S WISE.

06:25.428 --> 06:27.474
THAT LOOKS REMARKABLY
LIKE PETER.

06:27.561 --> 06:30.172
HEY, GUYS.
WHAT YOU DOING?

06:30.259 --> 06:33.262
OH, JUST BEING OPPRESSED
BY THE MAN -- THE USUAL.

06:33.349 --> 06:36.178
SOMETHING FOR THE CRAZY MAN
WHO HAS EVERYTHING?

06:36.265 --> 06:38.615
OH, THAT'S SWEET DARNELL,
MY TASTE-TESTER.

06:38.702 --> 06:40.356
YOU CAN NEVER BE
TOO CAREFUL.

06:40.443 --> 06:42.097
YOU IN DANGER, MOZZIE?

06:42.184 --> 06:44.273
I LIVE IN DANGER, SUIT.

06:44.360 --> 06:46.362
THIS WOULDN'T HAVE ANYTHING TO
DO WITH FRANK DE LUCA, WOULD IT?

06:47.972 --> 06:49.234
COME ON, GUYS.

06:49.321 --> 06:50.801
ORGANIZED CRIME'S
BEEN FOLLOWING DE LUCA.

06:50.888 --> 06:51.846
I KNOW HE WAS HERE.

06:54.065 --> 06:56.851
HE'S FORCING A MEET WITH MOZ
USING AN OLD FRIEND AS LEVERAGE.

06:56.938 --> 06:59.114
NEAL.
WHY?
WHAT DOES HE WANT WITH YOU?

06:59.201 --> 07:02.160
I-I'M A MAN OF MANY SECRETS,
BUT I AM GOING TO THAT MEETING.

07:02.247 --> 07:04.685
ABSOLUTELY NOT.
DE LUCA'S DANGEROUS.

07:04.772 --> 07:07.035
I-I'D LIKE TO SEE YOU
TRY AND STOP ME.

07:07.122 --> 07:09.690
[ SIREN CHIRPS ]CONSIDER YOURSELF
A PROTECTED WITNESS.

07:09.777 --> 07:11.343
YOU CAN'T DO THIS!OH, I CAN.

07:11.431 --> 07:13.520
WHAT DOES DE LUCA WANT
WITH YOU?
HE WANTS --

07:13.607 --> 07:15.086
DON'T SAY IT, NEAL.

07:15.173 --> 07:16.392
DE LUCA WANTS MOZZIE

07:16.479 --> 07:18.046
BECAUSE HE'S
THE DENTIST OF DETROIT.

07:18.133 --> 07:19.700
NEAL!
ET TU, BRUTE?

07:19.787 --> 07:20.962
ET TU?!

07:21.049 --> 07:22.920
I'M SORRY.
IT'S TO KEEP YOU SAFE.

07:23.007 --> 07:24.705
MOZZIE IS
THE DENTIST OF DETROIT?

07:24.792 --> 07:26.837
I KNOW. I'M STILL TRYING
TO WRAP MYHEAD AROUND IT.

07:26.924 --> 07:28.099
YOU KNOW, I RESENT
YOUR JUDGMENT

07:28.186 --> 07:29.536
AND YOUR MISGUIDED
MISUNDERSTANDING

07:29.623 --> 07:31.233
OF THINGS
YOU DO NOT UNDERSTAND...

07:31.320 --> 07:32.452
[ SIREN CHIRPS ]

07:35.629 --> 07:38.936
NEAL, THE DENTIST IS LINKED
TO HUNDREDS OF CRIMES

07:39.023 --> 07:41.286
GOING OVER DECADES --
SOME REALLY BAD STUFF.

07:41.373 --> 07:43.854
MOZZIE'S A LOT OF THINGS,
BUT HE'S NOT BAD.

07:43.941 --> 07:45.073
CAN YOU PROTECT HIM?

07:45.160 --> 07:47.336
I CAN...

07:47.423 --> 07:49.381
BUT I CAN'T IGNORE
WHAT HE'S DONE.

07:49.469 --> 07:51.819
[ CELL PHONE BEEPS, RINGING ]

07:51.906 --> 07:53.298
DIANA: Yeah, boss?

07:53.385 --> 07:55.213
DIANA, GET ME EVERYTHING
YOU CAN FIND

07:55.300 --> 07:56.476
ON THE DENTIST OF DETROIT.

07:56.563 --> 07:58.173
WE'VE GOT OUR NEXT CASE.

08:04.875 --> 08:06.094
ATTICA!

08:06.181 --> 08:07.356
HUNGER STRIKE!

08:07.443 --> 08:09.097
WHAT'S GOING ON, NEAL?VOW OF SILENCE!

08:09.184 --> 08:11.012
IT'S NOT WHAT YOU
THINK. HE GOT ON THE
BAD SIDE OF THE MOB.

08:11.099 --> 08:13.101
I DIDN'T KNOW HE DID IT
AS THE DENTIST.

08:13.188 --> 08:14.668
I DIDN'T.

08:14.755 --> 08:16.626
HE TOLD ME SOME OF THE STORY.
LET HIM TELL YOU, TOO.

08:16.713 --> 08:18.672
I KNOW WHY
THE CAGED BIRD SINGS!

08:18.759 --> 08:22.023
HOW MANY SUITS DO YOU HAVE
HIDING OUT THERE?

08:22.110 --> 08:23.938
NO.
IASK THE QUESTIONS.

08:24.025 --> 08:25.113
DID YOU FIND
MR. JEFFRIES YET?

08:25.200 --> 08:27.681
DOES HE EVEN HEAR ME?JUST...

08:27.768 --> 08:30.640
DETROIT POLICE
SEARCHED HIS HOME AND OFFICE.

08:30.727 --> 08:32.424
THEY DIDN'T FIND MUCH,
BUT HIS CAR IS MISSING.

08:32.512 --> 08:33.730
IT'S A GOOD THING, MOZ.

08:33.817 --> 08:35.689
DE LUCA PROBABLY CAME AROUND
ASKING QUESTIONS,

08:35.776 --> 08:36.994
AND MR. JEFFRIES FLED.

08:37.081 --> 08:40.955
THE DENTIST OF DETROIT --
SUSPECTED MASTERMIND

08:41.042 --> 08:43.697
IN AT LEAST THREE
MAJOR SECURITIES FRAUDS.

08:43.784 --> 08:46.874
I'VE ALSO GOT A LITANY
OF VIOLENT CRIMES --

08:46.961 --> 08:50.051
ASSAULT, BATTERY,
AGGRAVATED ASSAULT,

08:50.138 --> 08:51.966
ASSAULT WITH INTENT
TO INTIMIDATE --

08:52.053 --> 08:53.489
PAGE AFTER PAGE
OF THIS STUFF.

08:53.576 --> 08:55.447
ARE YOU THE DENTIST?

08:56.840 --> 08:58.233
NO COMMENT.

08:58.320 --> 09:02.498
[ SIGHS ] NEAL'S CONVINCED ME
TO HEAR YOU OUT

09:02.585 --> 09:04.369
SO I CAN DECIDE WHETHER OR NOT
TO BOOK YOU.

09:04.456 --> 09:06.067
TALK TO HIM, MOZ --

09:06.154 --> 09:08.156
IF NOT TO HELP YOURSELF,
THEN TO HELP JEFFRIES.

09:08.243 --> 09:10.158
JUST TELL HIM THE STORY.

09:11.899 --> 09:13.291
WE TALK
ABOUT JEFFRIES FIRST.

09:13.378 --> 09:15.163
FINE.

09:17.687 --> 09:18.993
START TALKING.

09:21.517 --> 09:24.476
DETROIT, 1969.

09:24.564 --> 09:27.436
WE JUST PUT A MAN ON THE MOON,
GAS WAS 35 CENTS,

09:27.523 --> 09:29.569
AND I WAS ORPHANED.

09:34.922 --> 09:37.054
HEY, THERE,
LITTLE MAN.

09:37.141 --> 09:39.187
Mozzie:
ISAAC JEFFRIES FOUND ME.

09:39.274 --> 09:40.580
Shh, shh, shh.

09:40.667 --> 09:43.757
IT'S OKAY.
IT'S OKAY.

09:43.844 --> 09:45.149
HEY, THERE.

09:45.236 --> 09:46.673
YOU WANT
YOUR LITTLE FRIEND?[ CRYING ]

09:46.760 --> 09:48.109
HE WAS THE BEST THING
THAT EVER HAPPENED TO ME.

09:48.196 --> 09:51.286
I SEE HIS NAME IS MOZART,
HUH?

09:51.373 --> 09:53.244
Shh, shh, shh!

09:53.331 --> 09:54.681
YOU'RE GONNA BE OKAY.

09:54.768 --> 09:57.161
[ CHILDREN SHOUTING PLAYFULLY ]

09:57.248 --> 09:58.772
AS YOU CAN IMAGINE,

09:58.859 --> 10:01.296
GROWING UP AN ORPHAN
IN 1970s DETROIT

10:01.383 --> 10:03.733
WASN'T ALL GUMDROPS
AND UNICORNS,

10:03.820 --> 10:06.344
ESPECIALLY FOR A SMALL KID WITH THICK GLASSES.

10:06.431 --> 10:07.650
DON'T LET HIM GET IT!

10:07.737 --> 10:09.043
THROW IT IN THE MUD!

10:10.610 --> 10:13.395
[ DISTORTED LAUGHTER ]

10:13.482 --> 10:15.571
LOOK, HIS EYE CAME OFF.

10:15.658 --> 10:18.008
NOW HE NEEDS GLASSES
LIKE YOU.

10:18.095 --> 10:23.187
THAT BEAR WAS THE ONLY THING I HAD LEFT OF MY REAL PARENTS.

10:23.274 --> 10:25.233
YOU'RE HAVING A HARD TIME
WITH THE OTHER KIDS, AREN'T YOU?

10:25.320 --> 10:26.713
YEAH.

10:26.800 --> 10:28.758
WELL,
THEY'RE INTIMIDATED

10:28.845 --> 10:31.500
'CAUSE YOU'RE SMARTER,
AND THEY KNOW IT.

10:31.587 --> 10:34.764
"THERE IS NO KNOWLEDGE
THAT IS NOT POWER."

10:34.851 --> 10:36.810
YOU KNOW WHO SAID THAT?UNH-UNH.

10:36.897 --> 10:39.682
RALPH WALDO EMERSON.

10:39.769 --> 10:43.120
NOW, YOU STRIVE FOR KNOWLEDGE,
USE WHAT YOU LEARN,

10:43.207 --> 10:44.992
AND YOU'LL ALWAYS STAY
AHEAD OF THEM.

10:45.079 --> 10:46.558
MR. JEFFRIES FIXED IT.

10:46.646 --> 10:49.083
HE WAS THE ONE PERSON
WHO LOOKED OUT FOR ME.

10:49.170 --> 10:52.260
THERE YOU ARE,
GOOD AS NEW --

10:52.347 --> 10:54.175
WELL, MAYBE
WITH A BIT MORE CHARACTER.

10:54.262 --> 10:55.437
[ CHUCKLES ]

10:55.524 --> 10:57.874
CHARACTER
DEFINES PERSONALITY,

10:57.961 --> 10:59.746
AND IN THAT DEPARTMENT,

10:59.833 --> 11:03.227
YOUR CUP RUNNETH OVER,
LITTLE MAN.

11:03.314 --> 11:05.186
FROM THAT DAY ON,

11:05.273 --> 11:08.668
I READ EVERYTHING I COULD GET MY HANDS ON --

11:08.755 --> 11:10.713
EMERSON'S "SELF-RELIANCE,"

11:10.800 --> 11:12.672
THOMAS PYNCHON'S "V.,"

11:12.759 --> 11:15.544
ERICH FROMM'S
"ESCAPE FROM FREEDOM,"

11:15.631 --> 11:17.111
DU PICQ'S "BATTLE STUDIES."

11:17.198 --> 11:18.634
I TOOK JEFFRIES' ADVICE

11:18.721 --> 11:21.158
AND USED THAT KNOWLEDGE
TO FIGHT MY OWN WARS.

11:21.245 --> 11:23.334
SERIOUSLY, I DON'T HAVE
ANY MONEY FOR YOU, BILLY.

11:23.421 --> 11:24.858
TRY KENNY NUSBAUM.

11:24.945 --> 11:27.034
I SAW HIM STEALING A $20
OUT OF LOCKER 9.

11:27.121 --> 11:28.339
OH, WAIT.

11:28.426 --> 11:30.951
LOCKER 9's YOURS,
ISN'T IT, BILLY?

11:32.082 --> 11:33.170
LET GO OF MY HAIR!

11:33.257 --> 11:34.650
Kenny:
OR YOU'LL DO WHAT?

11:34.737 --> 11:37.392
THOSE WITH NO EYES
TO READ READILY

11:37.479 --> 11:39.786
ARE DOOMED
TO THE WORST ERRORS...

11:39.873 --> 11:42.005
TO PARAPHRASE DU PICQ.

11:42.092 --> 11:44.051
I DIDN'T TAKE YOUR MONEY![ GRUNTS ]

11:44.138 --> 11:46.314
[ CHILDREN CHANTING
"FIGHT! FIGHT! FIGHT!" ]

11:47.968 --> 11:49.970
JEFFRIES SAVED ME.

11:50.057 --> 11:52.450
HE GAVE ME A LIFE,
AND HE TOLD ME HOW TO LIVE IT.

11:52.537 --> 11:54.583
DO YOU HAVE ANY IDEA
WHERE HE MIGHT BE?

11:54.670 --> 11:57.760
WELL, WE EXCHANGED SECRET
MESSAGES OVER THE YEARS,

11:57.847 --> 11:59.762
BUT...

11:59.849 --> 12:02.156
WAIT, WHEN THEY SEARCHED
HIS HOUSE,

12:02.243 --> 12:03.810
DID THEY FIND
ANY STUFFED ANIMALS?

12:03.897 --> 12:05.507
YEAH.

12:05.594 --> 12:07.770
YEAH, THEY, UH --
THE COPS THOUGHT IT WAS ODD

12:07.857 --> 12:09.903
UNTIL THEY REALIZED
HE WORKED AT A GROUP HOME.

12:09.990 --> 12:12.253
RIGHT HERE --
ELEPHANT, TIGER, BEAR.

12:12.340 --> 12:13.341
THE -- THE BEAR!

12:13.428 --> 12:14.385
THE BEAR IS ME.

12:14.472 --> 12:15.996
IT WAS HOLDING AN APPLE.

12:16.083 --> 12:17.954
THAT WAS A CLUE --
THE BIG APPLE.

12:18.041 --> 12:19.086
HE'S COMING HERE
TO WARN ME.

12:20.261 --> 12:22.350
YOU'RE...
SURE ABOUT THAT?

12:22.437 --> 12:24.569
I THINK I AM.

12:24.656 --> 12:25.875
THE FBI
WILL FIND JEFFRIES,

12:25.962 --> 12:27.572
AND WE'LL PUT HIM
UNDER PROTECTION.

12:27.659 --> 12:28.835
WHAT IF THEY
FIND HIM FIRST?

12:28.922 --> 12:30.575
I HAVE TO GO
TO DE LUCA'S MEETING.

12:30.662 --> 12:33.056
NO, MOZZIE, DE LUCA MAY HAVE
ALREADY KILLED ONE MAN.

12:33.143 --> 12:34.754
WE DON'T WANT TO ADD YOU
TO THAT LIST.

12:34.841 --> 12:36.364
THEY DON'T KNOW
WHAT THE DENTIST LOOKS LIKE.

12:36.451 --> 12:37.408
I COULD GO
IN MOZZIE'S PLACE.

12:37.495 --> 12:38.801
NEAL...

12:38.888 --> 12:41.108
YOU'LL NEVER PASS
AS THE DENTIST.

12:41.195 --> 12:42.109
I COULD BE
HIS ASSISTANT.

12:42.196 --> 12:43.414
THIS ISN'T YOUR FIGHT.

12:43.501 --> 12:44.851
NO, IT'S NOT.

12:44.938 --> 12:46.722
BUT YOU AREMY FRIEND.

12:48.550 --> 12:50.465
STAY PUT.

12:57.124 --> 12:58.603
MAN:
North sniper team set.

12:58.690 --> 13:00.127
MAN #2: Ground unit
moving into position.

13:01.650 --> 13:03.217
MAN #3:
South sniper team set.

13:03.304 --> 13:05.306
Peter: ALL RIGHT,
SNIPERS ARE IN POSITION.

13:05.393 --> 13:07.264
WE HAVE JONES STANDING BY
WITH S.W.A.T.

13:07.351 --> 13:09.266
YOU'LL BE TRANSMITTING
THROUGH THIS.

13:09.353 --> 13:11.965
ANY PROBLEMS,
MOZZIE'S WAITING BY THE PHONE.

13:12.052 --> 13:14.010
GOT IT.
DON'T WORRY, PETER.
[ SIGHS ]

13:14.097 --> 13:16.186
I'LL BE WATCHING
FROM THE CAR.

13:16.273 --> 13:17.753
ALL RIGHT.

13:27.458 --> 13:28.590
[ CAR DOORS CLOSE ]

13:28.677 --> 13:29.983
MR. DE LUCA?

13:30.070 --> 13:31.985
We've got eyes on de Luca.

13:32.072 --> 13:35.423
YOU -- I REMEMBER YOU
FROM THE WAREHOUSE.

13:35.510 --> 13:37.686
YOU'RE TOO YOUNG
TO BE THE DENTIST.

13:37.773 --> 13:40.036
I'M NOT THE DENTIST.
I'M HIS LIP MAN.

13:40.123 --> 13:41.472
OH, YOU'RE HIS LIP MAN.

13:41.559 --> 13:43.910
HE'S HIS LIP MAN.

13:43.997 --> 13:45.825
WELL,
I DO MY OWNTALKING.

13:45.912 --> 13:47.696
And my message goes directly
to The Dentist,

13:47.783 --> 13:49.089
not to some flunky,

13:49.176 --> 13:52.483
SO NO DENTIST, NO DEAL,
ALL RIGHT?

13:52.570 --> 13:55.269
HE'S A NO-SHOW.
JEFFRIES WILL BE MORTIFIED.

13:55.356 --> 13:56.748
HEY, HEY,
ALL RIGHT, ALL RIGHT, ALL RIGHT.

13:56.836 --> 13:58.794
HEY.
THE DENTIST IS HERE.

14:00.752 --> 14:02.319
NEAL,
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

14:02.406 --> 14:03.668
WHERE?

14:03.755 --> 14:05.975
BLACK SEDAN,
NORTH SIDE OF THE STREET.

14:07.629 --> 14:09.152
WELL,
THAT COULD BE ANYBODY.

14:09.239 --> 14:10.284
I'LL NEED SOME PROOF.

14:11.981 --> 14:13.200
OKAY.

14:17.160 --> 14:18.640
ASK HIM A QUESTION.

14:18.727 --> 14:19.859
[ CELL PHONE VIBRATING ]

14:22.992 --> 14:25.473
Diana, have Mozzie
take over this call.

14:28.302 --> 14:29.912
THE DENTIST IS IN.

14:29.999 --> 14:31.871
MR. DE LUCA
HAS A QUESTION FOR YOU.

14:31.958 --> 14:34.177
ASK HIM...

14:35.875 --> 14:37.877
...WHAT'S HIS FAVORITE
ICE CREAM?

14:39.487 --> 14:40.749
NEAL: Mr. De Luca
would like to know,

14:40.836 --> 14:42.533
what is
your favorite ice cream?

14:42.620 --> 14:43.708
SERIOUSLY?

14:45.319 --> 14:46.320
BUBBLE GUM.

14:46.407 --> 14:48.800
BUBBLE GUM.

14:55.416 --> 14:59.855
DENTIST PULLED A CON --
A BIG ONE -- ON MY FATHER.

14:59.942 --> 15:01.726
I WANT HIM TO PULL
THE SAME HUSTLE

15:01.813 --> 15:03.685
ON THIS GUY
HERE IN NEW YORK

15:03.772 --> 15:05.295
who, uh,
wasn't so friendly to me.

15:05.382 --> 15:07.167
WHO'S THE MARK?PATRICK O'LEARY.

15:07.254 --> 15:08.429
IRISH MOB.

15:08.516 --> 15:10.213
ALL THE DETAILS
ARE IN THERE.

15:18.961 --> 15:20.615
DE LUCA THINKS
O'LEARY'S RESPONSIBLE

15:20.702 --> 15:22.051
FOR HIS FATHER'S DEATH.

15:22.138 --> 15:23.618
RULE NUMBER ONE --
DON'T MESS WITH THE FAMILY.

15:23.705 --> 15:24.967
HE CAME ALL THE WAY HERE

15:25.054 --> 15:26.926
TO PUT THE DENTIST
IN THE MIDDLE OF A MOB WAR.

15:27.013 --> 15:29.102
MOZZIE GETS CAUGHT
IN THE CROSS FIRE.

15:29.189 --> 15:31.321
TWO BIRDS, ONE STONE.

15:31.408 --> 15:34.237
WHAT SORT OF CON DID MOZZIE PULL
TO HAVE DE LUCA SO PISSED?

15:34.324 --> 15:36.805
I DON'T KNOW, BUT IT INVOLVED
STEALING 500 GRAND

15:36.892 --> 15:38.241
FROM DE LUCA'S DAD.

15:38.328 --> 15:39.851
NO WONDER THEY'VE GOT IT OUT
FOR THE DENTIST.

15:39.939 --> 15:42.289
WHO THEY THINK IS YOU.

15:42.376 --> 15:44.073
WHAT'S THAT LOOK?
I DON'T LIKE THAT LOOK.

15:44.160 --> 15:45.770
DE LUCA WANTS THE DENTIST
TO RUN A CON.

15:45.857 --> 15:47.076
IF YOU
GO THROUGH WITH IT...

15:47.163 --> 15:48.338
AND PUT THE CASH
IN DE LUCA'S HAND,

15:48.425 --> 15:49.818
WE GOT HIM ON EXTORTION.

15:49.905 --> 15:51.907
DE LUCA GOES DOWN, AND MOZZIE
AND JEFFRIES ARE FREE.

15:51.994 --> 15:53.604
THAT'S WHY WE PAY YOU
THE BIG BUCKS...

15:54.692 --> 15:56.346
...IF WE PAID YOU.

15:56.433 --> 15:58.218
THINK WE CAN GET MOZZIE
TO TELL US HOW HE DID IT?

15:58.305 --> 15:59.959
YOU THREATEN HIM
WITH A FUTURE OF TOILET WINE,

16:00.046 --> 16:01.221
AND HE WILL SING
LIKE A CANARY.

16:01.308 --> 16:03.614
I CAN SCARE HIM
PRETTY GOOD.

16:09.969 --> 16:11.318
BEFORE
I TELL YOU ANYTHING,

16:11.405 --> 16:12.754
I WANT COMPLETE IMMUNITY

16:12.841 --> 16:14.321
AND THE TRUTH
BEHIND DARPA's --

16:14.408 --> 16:16.018
NO AND NO.

16:16.105 --> 16:18.803
YOU ARE STILL A SUSPECT
IN A DOZEN OTHER CRIMES.

16:18.890 --> 16:20.109
START TALKING.

16:20.196 --> 16:22.111
FINE.

16:22.198 --> 16:23.939
BUT THE STATUTE
OF LIMITATION

16:24.026 --> 16:26.463
PROTECTS CRIMES
COMMITTED BY A MINOR.

16:26.550 --> 16:28.770
MINOR?
HOW LONG AGO DID THIS HAPPEN?

16:30.772 --> 16:32.295
WHEN I WAS 12.

16:32.382 --> 16:34.950
YOU WERE 12 WHEN YOU STOLE
500 GRAND FROM THE DETROIT MOB?

16:35.037 --> 16:36.343
GIFTED CHILD.

16:36.430 --> 16:38.649
THERE'S YOUR IMMUNITY.
TALK.

16:39.781 --> 16:42.958
LOOK,
WHEN YOU'RE AN ORPHAN,

16:43.045 --> 16:45.700
A-A FAMILY IS LIKE
YOUR HOLY GRAIL.

16:45.787 --> 16:49.573
MR. JEFFRIES WORKED REALLY HARD
TO FIND ME ONE, AND HE DID,

16:49.660 --> 16:54.013
A WONDERFUL URBANE COUPLE
FROM STERLING HEIGHTS.

16:54.100 --> 16:56.450
THEY TAUGHT ME ABOUT
ALL THE FINEST THINGS IN LIFE --

16:56.537 --> 16:58.887
MUSIC, ART.

16:58.974 --> 17:01.107
THEY WERE QUITE DECENT...

17:03.283 --> 17:06.112
...FOR PEOPLE
WHO WORE SUITS.

17:08.070 --> 17:09.419
WHAT WENT WRONG?

17:09.506 --> 17:11.639
THEY HAD A SON --

17:11.726 --> 17:13.902
AN ONLY CHILD.

17:13.989 --> 17:16.165
THEIR SON --
HE GOT JEALOUS,

17:16.252 --> 17:18.820
SO HE STOLE A PRICELESS
FAMILY HEIRLOOM

17:18.907 --> 17:22.345
AND PINNED THE CRIME ON ME,
AND I GOT SCARED...

17:22.432 --> 17:24.086
RAN AWAY.

17:24.173 --> 17:27.263
I HIT THE STREETS.

17:27.350 --> 17:30.049
I GOT A JOB MAKING BOOK
FOR A NUMBERS GUY.

17:30.136 --> 17:32.921
BEFORE LONG, I KNEW THE BUSINESS BETTER THAN HE DID.

17:33.008 --> 17:35.619
I'M TELLIN' YOU, BIGGIE,
IF WE OPEN A POLICY BANK,

17:35.706 --> 17:38.100
WE CAN CENTRALIZE
WHERE RUNNERS REPORT BETS,

17:38.187 --> 17:41.060
WE CAN HIRE MORE PEOPLE,
AND WE CAN TRIPLE OUR PROFITS.

17:41.147 --> 17:43.410
AH! GET LOST, KID.

17:43.497 --> 17:46.848
BIGGIE? SERIOUSLY?

17:46.935 --> 17:49.503
PROBLEM WAS,
WHO'S GONNA TRUST A KID?

17:49.590 --> 17:51.461
ADULTS LIKE TO FEEL SUPERIOR.

17:51.548 --> 17:53.942
THEY WANT TO THINK THEY'RE SMARTER THAN EVERYONE ELSE.

17:54.029 --> 17:55.857
SO I LEARNED
THE ART OF THE CON.

17:57.641 --> 17:59.730
DANG, BRUNO,
SIX IN A ROW!

17:59.817 --> 18:01.471
SOMETIMES I WISH
I WORKED FOR SOMEONE

18:01.558 --> 18:02.820
WHO KNEW WHAT HE WAS DOING,

18:02.907 --> 18:04.431
SOMEONE WITH SOME BRAINS,
YOU KNOW?

18:04.518 --> 18:05.432
LIKE YOU.

18:07.173 --> 18:10.480
OH, BRUNO,
NOT THE HAIR, MAN.

18:10.567 --> 18:11.916
YOU GOT YOURSELF A PATSY.

18:12.003 --> 18:13.831
YOU USE WHAT YOU LEARN.

18:13.918 --> 18:16.051
I TALKED BRUNO INTO OPENING A BACK OFFICE

18:16.138 --> 18:17.400
IN A BETTING PARLOR.

18:17.487 --> 18:19.533
HE WAS THE PUBLIC FACE
OF THE DENTIST.

18:19.620 --> 18:21.448
I WAS THE BRAINS.

18:21.535 --> 18:23.014
WHY "THE DENTIST"?

18:23.102 --> 18:24.451
I WAS 12.

18:24.538 --> 18:26.931
A DENTIST WAS THE SCARIEST THING
I COULD THINK OF,

18:27.018 --> 18:28.716
AND...IT WORKED.

18:28.803 --> 18:30.979
TOGETHER, BRUNO AND I

18:31.066 --> 18:32.937
RAN THE BIGGEST
STREET LOTTERY IN TOWN,

18:33.024 --> 18:35.897
HAD RUNNERS WORKING FOR US ALL OVER THE CITY.

18:35.984 --> 18:37.551
WHOA.

18:37.638 --> 18:40.554
THE DENTIST IS BUSY.
COME BACK LATER.

18:40.641 --> 18:43.296
PEOPLE LOVED US...

18:43.383 --> 18:46.429
EXCEPT THE ONES
WHO OWED US MONEY.

18:46.516 --> 18:48.866
THAT'S WHEN DE LUCA
CAME IN.

18:48.953 --> 18:51.173
HE DIDN'T LIKE ME
CUTTING INTO HIS PROFITS.

18:51.260 --> 18:53.393
FRANKIE JR.,
STAY BY THE CAR.

18:56.570 --> 18:59.486
DE LUCA CAUGHT WIND
OF THE DENTIST,

18:59.573 --> 19:01.923
THREATENED BRUNO
INTO CLOSING SHOP.

19:02.010 --> 19:05.013
WHAT ARE YOU LOOKING AT?

19:05.100 --> 19:06.928
Mozzie:
I WANTED PAYBACK,

19:07.015 --> 19:09.409
SO I GOT DE LUCA SR.
ON A WIRE CON.

19:09.496 --> 19:12.194
HE WENT IN FOR 500 LARGE.

19:12.281 --> 19:14.109
HOW'D HE FIND OUT YOU WERE
THE KID BEHIND THE CURTAIN?

19:14.196 --> 19:15.937
BRUNO SOLD ME OUT.

19:16.024 --> 19:17.634
HE TOLD THEM
I WAS THE DENTIST.

19:17.721 --> 19:20.681
I HAD TO RETIRE THE MONIKER --
NO MORE DENTIST.

19:20.768 --> 19:23.553
I TOOK THE MONEY,
LEFT FOR NEW YORK,

19:23.640 --> 19:25.468
AND BECAME A NEW PERSON.

19:25.555 --> 19:27.340
ALL RIGHT,
WHAT ABOUT EVERYTHING

19:27.427 --> 19:29.342
ATTRIBUTED TO THE DENTIST
SINCE THEN?

19:29.429 --> 19:31.431
DE LUCA DIDN'T WANT
THE WORLD TO KNOW

19:31.518 --> 19:33.781
HE'D BEEN TAKEN
BY A PREPUBESCENT GRIFTER.

19:33.868 --> 19:35.696
HE STARTED THE RUMOR
THAT THE DENTIST WAS SUPERMAN.

19:35.783 --> 19:37.001
YEP.

19:37.088 --> 19:39.308
THE DENTIST
BECAME THE PERFECT PATSY

19:39.395 --> 19:41.615
FOR EVERY CRIMINAL
IN THE NORTHEAST.

19:41.702 --> 19:43.878
YOU'RE A LIVING
CONSPIRACY THEORY.

19:43.965 --> 19:46.010
SEE?
THEY DOEXIST.

19:46.097 --> 19:47.708
Jones: OHIO TURNPIKE
CLOCKED JEFFRIES' CAR

19:47.795 --> 19:49.318
RUNNING A TOLL
A COUPLE OF HOURS AGO.

19:49.405 --> 19:51.277
MR. JEFFRIES
WOULD NEVER RUN A TOLL.

19:51.364 --> 19:53.279
HE'S A VERY
CONSCIENTIOUS DRIVER.

19:53.366 --> 19:55.455
WAIT!
THAT'S ANOTHER CLUE!

19:55.542 --> 19:57.021
DO THEY HAVE A PHOTO?

19:57.108 --> 19:59.633
IT'S ON ITS WAY.

19:59.720 --> 20:01.548
LOOK, MOZZIE'S GIVEN US
EVERYTHING WE NEED

20:01.635 --> 20:02.984
TO RUN THE CON
ON O'LEARY.

20:03.071 --> 20:04.028
WHAT ARE YOU GONNA DO
WITH HIM NOW?

20:04.115 --> 20:05.682
[ SIGHS ]

20:05.769 --> 20:08.424
I'M GONNA CHECK AND RECHECK
EVERY CASE IN THIS FILE.

20:08.511 --> 20:09.817
YOUR STORY BETTER HOLD UP.

20:09.904 --> 20:10.861
IT WILL.

20:10.948 --> 20:12.167
YOU'RE IN DANGER,

20:12.254 --> 20:14.169
AND YOU'RE A LIABILITY
TO US ON THE STREET.

20:14.256 --> 20:15.823
JONES,
TAKE HIM TO A SAFE HOUSE.

20:15.910 --> 20:18.913
AN FBI-MONITORED
SAFE HOUSE?

20:19.000 --> 20:21.132
THAT'S LEGALIZED TORTURE!

20:21.220 --> 20:23.657
IT'S THAT, OR I SET YOU IN
LOCKDOWN UNTIL THIS IS OVER.

20:23.744 --> 20:24.919
AH, SAFE HOUSE IT IS.

20:25.006 --> 20:27.182
BUT -- BUT I HAVE DEMANDS.

20:27.269 --> 20:30.925
MY ATOPIC ECZEMA REQUIRES
CUSTOM-MADE SILK PAJAMAS.

20:31.012 --> 20:34.189
READING GLASSES, SLIPPERS,
SLEEP MACHINE -- ALL VITAL.

20:34.276 --> 20:36.017
OH, AND -- AND
I HAVE SOFT GUMS,

20:36.104 --> 20:37.845
SO I'LL BE NEEDING
MY ELECTRONIC TOOTHBRUSH.

20:37.932 --> 20:39.586
DO WE LOOK LIKE
YOUR ERRAND BOYS?

20:39.673 --> 20:41.152
FINE.
THEN NO COMPLAINTS

20:41.240 --> 20:43.329
WHEN I'M FORCED TO SLEEP
IN THE NUDE TONIGHT.

20:44.721 --> 20:46.810
MAKE A LIST.
I'LL MAKE A LIST.

20:50.379 --> 20:53.426
Jones: YOU'RE GIVING ME
A HEADACHE.

20:53.513 --> 20:55.341
THIS ISN'T EXACTLY THE PLAZA
OF SAFE HOUSES, IS IT?

20:55.428 --> 20:57.430
THE MATTRESS
ISN'T HYPOALLERGENIC.

20:57.517 --> 20:59.693
I SAW A DEAD MOUSE
ON THE BATHROOM RADIATOR.

20:59.780 --> 21:01.347
AH, LUCKY BASTARD GOT OUT
WHILE HE COULD.

21:01.434 --> 21:02.739
[ DOOR OPENS ]

21:02.826 --> 21:04.654
ALL RIGHT, HERE ARE THE ITEMS
YOU REQUESTED, MOZ.

21:04.741 --> 21:06.308
OH, GREAT.
RIGHT HERE.

21:06.395 --> 21:08.615
THANKS.

21:08.702 --> 21:09.964
OH, YOU TOUCH ANYTHING,

21:10.051 --> 21:11.052
AND YOU'LL BE HEARING
FROM MY LAWYER.

21:11.139 --> 21:12.706
YOU AREYOUR LAWYER.SCARED?

21:12.793 --> 21:14.273
OOH.

21:14.360 --> 21:15.926
GOT PICTURES OF JEFFRIES
AT THE TOLL.

21:16.013 --> 21:18.320
OH, LET ME SEE THAT.

21:18.407 --> 21:19.974
LOOK WHAT'S ON
THE DASHBOARD.

21:20.061 --> 21:22.063
Neal:
YEAH, A BOOK, A CD.

21:22.150 --> 21:24.848
A PARTICULAR BOOK,
A PARTICULAR CD.

21:24.935 --> 21:26.110
"ESCAPE FROM FREEDOM."

21:26.197 --> 21:27.286
A MASTERPIECE.

21:27.373 --> 21:29.940
AND THE CD --
"LA FEMME."

21:30.027 --> 21:31.942
FREEDOM. FEMME.

21:32.029 --> 21:33.901
LADY LIBERTY.YES!

21:33.988 --> 21:35.642
HE'LL BE GOING TO
THE STATUE OF LIBERTY
WHEN HE GETS HERE.

21:38.775 --> 21:40.734
I-I GUESS IT'S WORTH
CHECKING OUT.

21:40.821 --> 21:42.518
YOU GUESS?

21:42.605 --> 21:44.694
YOU SEE WHAT I HAVE TO
PUT UP WITH BECAUSE OF YOU?

21:44.781 --> 21:46.827
HOW LONG DO I HAVE TO STAY
IN THIS STYGIAN LIMBO?

21:46.914 --> 21:48.568
YOU WON'T BE SAFE
UNTIL WE RUN THE CON

21:48.655 --> 21:50.178
AND GET DE LUCA
IN CUFFS, OKAY?

21:50.265 --> 21:53.007
I BEG OF YOU, HURRY,
FOR THE SAKE OF MY SANITY.

21:53.094 --> 21:54.443
And mine.

22:00.406 --> 22:02.625
Peter: THIS IS OUR MARK --
PATRICK O'LEARY.

22:02.712 --> 22:04.584
THOSE OF YOU FROM
ORGANIZED CRIME KNOW HIM WELL.

22:04.671 --> 22:06.281
DE LUCA
PLANS TO SCAM O'LEARY

22:06.368 --> 22:08.762
FOR HALF A MIL
IN A WIRE CON

22:08.849 --> 22:10.459
AND PIN IT
ON THE DENTIST.

22:10.546 --> 22:12.374
THIS IS OUR CHANCE
TO TAKE THEM BOTH DOWN

22:12.461 --> 22:14.028
AND STOP A MOB WAR.

22:14.115 --> 22:16.900
DE LUCA IS COERCING THE DENTIST
INTO RUNNING THE CON FOR HIM.

22:16.987 --> 22:18.249
NOW, UNFORTUNATELY,

22:18.337 --> 22:20.817
DE LUCA WANTS HIS GUY
PRESENT AT THE SCAM

22:20.904 --> 22:22.732
TO MAKE SURE THINGS
ARE RUNNING SMOOTHLY.

22:22.819 --> 22:24.908
WHICH MEANS WE'LL HAVE TO
GO THROUGH WITH THE WIRE CON

22:24.995 --> 22:26.780
IF WE'RE GONNA PUT THE CASH
IN DE LUCA'S HANDS.

22:26.867 --> 22:28.303
I'LL NEED A HALF DOZEN
FLAT SCREENS,

22:28.390 --> 22:29.826
PROFESSIONAL
SATELLITE EQUIPMENT,

22:29.913 --> 22:31.393
AND VIDEO-DELAYING SOFTWARE.

22:31.480 --> 22:34.091
WE'RE GONNA BUILD A BETTING SITE
TO RIVAL THE COMPETITION.

22:34.178 --> 22:35.354
HOW DO WE GET
O'LEARY THERE?

22:35.441 --> 22:36.790
ELIMINATE
THE COMPETITION.

22:42.186 --> 22:43.579
[ SIREN WAILS ]

22:43.666 --> 22:45.189
COME ON, GUYS.

22:45.276 --> 22:47.148
ENJOY YOUR RIDE
DOWNTOWN, GENTLEMEN.

22:49.193 --> 22:52.196
WHAT'S THIS --
SOME KIND OF BUST?

22:52.283 --> 22:54.503
ILLEGAL OFF-TRACK BETTING.
SITE'S CLOSED.

22:54.590 --> 22:56.462
ANONYMOUS TIP
WAS CALLED IN.

22:56.549 --> 22:57.593
YOU A CUSTOMER?

22:57.680 --> 22:59.813
INNOCENT BYSTANDER.

22:59.900 --> 23:01.423
BESIDES,
YOUR CAR LOOKS FILLED UP.

23:01.510 --> 23:03.077
WE CAN MAKE SOME ROOM.

23:03.164 --> 23:04.774
IT CAN TOW
UP TO 5,000 POUNDS.

23:04.861 --> 23:06.472
[ CHUCKLES ]

23:06.559 --> 23:08.430
COME ON, BIG FELLA.
WATCH YOUR HEAD.

23:08.517 --> 23:11.651
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER,
SIRENS WAILING ]

23:13.696 --> 23:16.482
SORRY TO HEAR ABOUT YOUR PLACE,
O'LEARY.

23:18.701 --> 23:20.181
IF YOU NEED
SOMETHING NEW...

23:23.663 --> 23:26.056
YOU'RE THE RAT
WHO PROBABLY CALLED THE FEDS.

23:26.143 --> 23:27.493
THAT WOULD BE MY BOSS.

23:27.580 --> 23:29.886
HE'S TRYING TO
DRIVE BUSINESS HIS WAY.

23:29.973 --> 23:32.889
THOSE WERE MY FRIENDS.
TELL YOUR BOSS HE'LL BE SORRY.

23:32.976 --> 23:35.196
SURE THING...

23:35.283 --> 23:37.677
OR I COULD HELP YOU SEND
A STRONGER MESSAGE.

23:39.722 --> 23:40.984
WHAT DOES THAT MEAN?

23:41.071 --> 23:43.683
MY BOSS HAS ME PICKING UP STRAYS
ON THE SIDEWALK

23:43.770 --> 23:45.249
LIKE A BENCH ADVERTISEMENT.

23:45.336 --> 23:46.860
WE HAVE OUR DIFFERENCES.

23:46.947 --> 23:48.731
SO YOU'RE ON THE OUTS
WITH YOUR BOSS.
WHAT DO I CARE?

23:48.818 --> 23:50.211
BECAUSE I CAN HELP YOU
TAKE HIM DOWN.

23:50.298 --> 23:51.995
WHO ARE YOU?

23:52.082 --> 23:55.042
A LIP MAN TRYING TO MOVE UP
IN THE WORLD.

23:57.914 --> 23:59.394
HOW 'BOUT WE TAKE
THIS CONVERSATION

23:59.481 --> 24:00.700
SOMEWHERE
A LITTLE MORE PRIVATE?

24:08.447 --> 24:10.579
I STILL CAN'T BELIEVE
YOU'VE GOT MOZZIE

24:10.666 --> 24:12.712
IN AN FBI-MONITORED HOTEL.

24:12.799 --> 24:14.235
WE CALL IT A SAFE HOUSE,

24:14.322 --> 24:16.455
AND DIANA'S HEADED THERE
FOR COMPANY.

24:16.542 --> 24:17.891
[ CHUCKLES ]
OOH, MUFFINS.

24:17.978 --> 24:19.588
AH, AH, NO.
THESE ARE FOR MOZZIE.

24:19.675 --> 24:21.677
OH, SERIOUSLY? YOU REALLY
FEEL THAT BAD FOR HIM?

24:21.764 --> 24:23.592
HIM, DIANA COOPED UP TOGETHER
IN THAT ROOM...

24:23.679 --> 24:24.985
YOU'RE AMUSED
BY ALL THIS.
[ LAUGHS ]

24:25.072 --> 24:26.943
YOU JUST WANT TO GO THERE
ON YOUR OWN, DON'T YOU?

24:27.030 --> 24:28.423
YEAH.
CAN YOU BLAME ME?

24:28.510 --> 24:31.034
NO. BUT YOU'LL NEED PERMISSION
FROM THE HEAD AGENT

24:31.121 --> 24:32.209
IF YOU WANT TO SEE HIM.

24:32.296 --> 24:33.863
OH, REALLY?
MM-HMM.

24:33.950 --> 24:34.908
MM.

24:36.823 --> 24:38.694
PLEASE?

24:38.781 --> 24:40.479
PERMISSION GRANTED.
THANK YOU.

24:40.566 --> 24:41.654
MM.

24:41.741 --> 24:43.220
ALL RIGHT, NOW,
ON A SERIOUS NOTE,

24:43.307 --> 24:45.092
THIS CASE THAT YOU'RE DOING
WITH NEAL -- IS IT DANGEROUS?

24:45.179 --> 24:46.876
NO, IT'S MORE FUN
THAN DANGEROUS.

24:46.963 --> 24:48.530
YOU SAW "THE STING,"
RIGHT?

24:48.617 --> 24:50.706
YEAH, SOMETHING TO DO
WITH HORSES AND BETTING.

24:50.793 --> 24:53.143
MM-HMM.IF THE MOB'S INVOLVED,
HOW COULD IT NOT BE DANGEROUS?

24:53.230 --> 24:54.623
UH...

24:54.710 --> 24:56.756
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]DOOR'S OPEN, NEAL.

24:59.672 --> 25:01.674
HEY.
HEY.
HEY!

25:01.761 --> 25:03.458
WHO KNEW THE BALL AND CHAIN
CLEANED UP SO NICE?

25:03.545 --> 25:05.025
AH, YOU DON'T LOOK SO BAD
YOURSELF.

25:05.112 --> 25:06.592
SO, WHO'S NEWMAN
AND WHO'S REDFORD?

25:06.679 --> 25:07.897
I'M NEWMAN.
HE'S REDFORD.

25:07.984 --> 25:09.551
DID YOU TALK
TO DE LUCA?

25:09.638 --> 25:11.684
YEAH, HE'S DROPPING LEO
AT THE PARLOR IN AN HOUR.

25:11.771 --> 25:13.686
WE SHOULD GO.OH, WAIT.
BEFORE YOU GO, HOLD ON.

25:13.773 --> 25:14.991
I GOT TO GET THIS.

25:15.078 --> 25:16.993
ALL RIGHT, PROM PICTURE.

25:17.080 --> 25:18.081
SAY "CHEESE."

25:18.168 --> 25:19.213
Both: CHEESE.

25:19.300 --> 25:21.084
BEAUTIFUL.
BE SAFE, PLEASE.

25:21.171 --> 25:22.651
WE WILL.

25:25.393 --> 25:26.916
WHAT DO YOU SAY,
NEWMAN?

25:27.003 --> 25:29.484
YOU READY TO SCAM HALF A MILLION
DOLLARS FOR THE DETROIT MOB?

25:29.571 --> 25:30.790
LET'S GO, KID.

25:36.665 --> 25:38.798
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

25:49.243 --> 25:50.549
NOT A BAD SETUP.

25:50.636 --> 25:52.072
GLAD YOU LIKE IT.

25:52.159 --> 25:54.074
BUILDING IT
WAS LIKE PULLING TEETH.

25:54.161 --> 25:55.336
DENTIST HUMOR.

25:55.423 --> 25:57.773
YOU'RE ENJOYING YOURSELF.YEAH.

25:57.860 --> 26:00.297
LOOKS LIKE
WE GOT COMPANY.

26:00.384 --> 26:01.995
THERE'S DE LUCA'S GUY.

26:02.082 --> 26:03.170
ALL RIGHT, I'M ON IT.

26:07.391 --> 26:08.697
LOOKS LIKE
THE KIND OF PLACE

26:08.784 --> 26:10.090
SOMEONE COULD LOSE
A LOT OF MONEY.
MM-HMM.

26:10.177 --> 26:11.831
O'LEARY CLOSE?

26:11.918 --> 26:13.746
YEAH, OUR GUYS CLOCKED
HIM LEAVING HIS OFFICE
10 MINUTES AGO.

26:13.833 --> 26:15.138
WELL, BY THE TIME
HE GETS HERE,

26:15.225 --> 26:16.966
THERE'S GONNA BE FIVE RACES LEFT
ON THE CARD.

26:17.053 --> 26:18.359
THAT'S FIVE CHANCES
TO GET THE MONEY.

26:18.446 --> 26:19.534
CAN YOU DO IT?

26:19.621 --> 26:21.101
YEAH.

26:21.188 --> 26:22.755
[ GLASSES CLINK ]

26:22.842 --> 26:25.105
YOU KNOW, YOU COULD HAVE AT
LEAST BAKED A FILE INTO THESE.

26:25.192 --> 26:26.497
OH, PLEASE.

26:26.585 --> 26:27.760
I DON'T THINK THEY HAVE
LOVE SEATS IN THE JOINT.

26:27.847 --> 26:29.457
OH, THE JOINT?

26:29.544 --> 26:31.764
OH, DO YOU KNOW YOUR WAY AROUND
THE BIG HOUSE, DO YOU?

26:31.851 --> 26:34.593
I MAY HAVE SPENT SOME TIME
IN JAIL ONCE...

26:34.680 --> 26:35.942
OR TWICE.

26:36.029 --> 26:37.508
A REPEAT OFFENDER?

26:37.596 --> 26:39.946
THE FIRST TIME,
I GOT CAUGHT WITH A FAKE I.D.

26:40.033 --> 26:41.425
"ALLEGEDLY."
NEVER CONFIRM.

26:41.512 --> 26:43.079
RIGHT.
AND THE SECOND TIME?

26:43.166 --> 26:46.953
SECOND TIME, I ALLEGEDLY
STREAKED ACROSS CAMPUS.

26:47.040 --> 26:48.737
MRS. SUIT!
[ CHUCKLES ]

26:48.824 --> 26:50.478
WELL, IT WAS COLLEGE.
I LOST A BET.

26:50.565 --> 26:52.088
DOES THE HUSBAND KNOW
ABOUT THIS?

26:52.175 --> 26:53.699
HE MIGHT KNOW
ABOUT ONE OF THEM.

26:53.786 --> 26:55.309
I'LL LET YOU GUESS
WHICH ONE HE KNOWS.

26:55.396 --> 26:56.615
[ CHUCKLES ]

26:56.702 --> 26:58.094
ALL RIGHT,
SO, TELL ME...

26:58.181 --> 27:00.270
ABOUT THESE DE LUCAS THAT MY
HUSBAND'S MEETING WITH, HUH?

27:00.357 --> 27:01.489
HE'S A KILLER.

27:01.576 --> 27:03.665
I-I WAS 12,
AND I CAN ONLY IMAGINE

27:03.752 --> 27:05.536
WHAT THEY WOULD HAVE DONE TO ME,
GIVEN THE CHANCE.

27:05.624 --> 27:08.888
THAT'S WHY I LEFT DETROIT
AND CHANGED MY NAME.

27:08.975 --> 27:10.237
OH.

27:10.324 --> 27:12.326
UM...GIN.

27:12.413 --> 27:14.763
SO, YOU JUST KEPT RUNNING
FROM THE DE LUCAS?

27:14.850 --> 27:16.591
I MEAN, HAVE YOU THOUGHT
ABOUT CONFRONTING THEM?

27:16.678 --> 27:18.724
PUTTING AN END
TO THIS WHOLE FEUD FOR GOOD?

27:18.811 --> 27:19.986
YEAH.

27:20.073 --> 27:22.118
I HADN'T.

27:22.205 --> 27:24.294
BUT NOW THEY'RE THREATENING
PEOPLE I CARE ABOUT.

27:24.381 --> 27:26.427
IF ANYONE SHOULD BE TAKING
A BULLET FROM DE LUCA,

27:26.514 --> 27:27.646
IT SHOULD BE ME.

27:27.733 --> 27:28.864
[ DOOR OPENS ]

27:30.866 --> 27:32.041
I MISS ANYTHING?

27:32.128 --> 27:33.739
HE SET THE BED
ON FIRE?

27:33.826 --> 27:35.915
NO, NO.
HE BEHAVED.

27:36.002 --> 27:37.220
MM.

27:37.307 --> 27:39.875
I'M GONNA --
I'M GONNA GET GOING.

27:39.962 --> 27:42.312
ELIZABETH, UM...

27:42.399 --> 27:45.098
PETER WILL BE FINE.

27:45.185 --> 27:48.231
YEAH, I KNOW HE WILL.

27:48.318 --> 27:50.103
[ CHUCKLES ]
BYE. I'LL CALL YOU.

27:51.365 --> 27:53.541
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

27:53.628 --> 27:56.109
I NEED SOME FRESH MELON.

27:58.154 --> 28:00.635
[ WAND BEEPS ]

28:00.722 --> 28:03.072
MR. O'LEARY,
DELIGHTED TO HAVE YOU.

28:03.159 --> 28:04.508
MY REGULAR PLACE
WAS SHUT DOWN.

28:04.595 --> 28:05.727
SHAME.

28:05.814 --> 28:08.774
WE'LL NEED TO CHECK
YOUR BRIEFCASE.

28:16.085 --> 28:18.131
[ BRIEFCASE CLOSES,
LATCHES CLICK ]

28:18.218 --> 28:19.872
MY ASSOCIATE
WILL SHOW YOU AROUND.

28:19.959 --> 28:23.310
HAVE A GOOD TIME.

28:23.397 --> 28:25.181
SO, WALK ME
THROUGH THIS.

28:25.268 --> 28:27.662
I INSTALLED A WORM
ON THE CENTRAL COMPUTER

28:27.749 --> 28:29.272
THAT DELAYS EVERY FEED.

28:29.359 --> 28:31.274
WE'LL GET THE RACE RESULTS
THREE MINUTES BEFORE MY BOSS,

28:31.361 --> 28:33.712
GIVING US A SMALL WINDOW
TO PLACE THE BET.

28:35.801 --> 28:37.672
HE'S BOUND TO REALIZE
THE FEED'S DELAYED.

28:37.759 --> 28:39.979
YEAH, WHICH IS WHY WE HAVE
TO HIT IT HARD AND FAST
IF WE'RE GONNA DO THIS.

28:41.850 --> 28:44.897
DESKTOP DAN'S ABOUT TO MAKE
A BREAK IN THE FINAL FURLONG.

28:44.984 --> 28:47.073
Announcer: IT'S TURNCOAT JENNY IN THE LEAD,

28:47.160 --> 28:49.510
WITH JACKBOOT BOB HOT ON THE HEELS OF DESKTOP DAN.

28:49.597 --> 28:51.817
AND DESKTOP DAN'S MAKING A BREAK ON THE INSIDE!

28:51.904 --> 28:52.948
TURNCOAT JENNY
STILL OUT FRONT,

28:53.035 --> 28:54.907
BUT HERE COMES DESKTOP DAN.

28:54.994 --> 28:56.909
THEY'RE ONE, TWO.
NOW NECK AND NECK.

28:56.996 --> 28:59.694
AND IT'S DESKTOP DAN
FOR THE WIN!

28:59.781 --> 29:01.087
[ LAUGHS ][ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

29:01.174 --> 29:02.349
SECOND PLACE
GOES TO TURNCOAT JENNY...

29:02.436 --> 29:04.612
THE HATCHET TO WIN
AT FINGER LAKES

29:04.699 --> 29:06.962
WITH POINSETTIA
COMING IN SECOND.

29:07.049 --> 29:09.878
A STRAIGHT EXACTA BET
OF 20 G's WILL NET YOU $600,000.

29:09.965 --> 29:12.054
FIVE RACES LEFT AND COUNTING.
ARE YOU IN?

29:20.149 --> 29:24.110
FINGER LAKES, SEVENTH RACE,
STRAIGHT EXACTA.

29:24.197 --> 29:27.069
HATCHET TO WIN,
POINSEDDIA IS SECOND.

29:27.156 --> 29:28.244
WAGER...

29:30.681 --> 29:34.294
$5,000 WAGER.

29:34.381 --> 29:35.469
[ LATCHES CLICK ]

29:38.602 --> 29:40.735
ALL BETS ARE CLOSED.

29:48.308 --> 29:50.092
5 GRAND'S
THE MINIMUM BET.

29:50.179 --> 29:52.616
YOU GOT A LOT MORE
THAN THAT ON YOU.

29:52.703 --> 29:55.097
SLOW AND STEADY
WINS THE RACE, RIGHT, BOYO?

29:57.578 --> 30:00.102
AND THEY'RE OFF!

30:00.189 --> 30:02.844
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

30:02.931 --> 30:05.673
[ SIGHS ]

30:05.760 --> 30:07.283
ANY WORD
ON MR. JEFFRIES?

30:07.370 --> 30:09.416
WE'VE GOT AGENTS
CONTINUALLY CHECKING

30:09.503 --> 30:11.287
THE LIBERTY FERRY --
NOTHING SO FAR.

30:11.374 --> 30:14.247
MY MELON'S LATE.

30:14.334 --> 30:15.814
YEAH, WELL,
WE'VE GOT BETTER THINGS TO DO

30:15.901 --> 30:17.250
THAN WORRY
ABOUT YOUR SCHEDULED FEEDING.

30:17.337 --> 30:18.991
I NEED
MY AFTERNOON RESPITE.

30:19.078 --> 30:20.819
I CAN'T SLEEP
WITHOUT PARTAKING OF MELON.

30:20.906 --> 30:22.690
THEN YOU CAN'T SLEEP.[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

30:22.777 --> 30:23.909
PLEASE LET THAT BE
YOUR MELON.

30:25.388 --> 30:26.694
HEY.
HEY.

30:26.781 --> 30:28.391
SORRY I'M LATE.

30:28.478 --> 30:29.958
THE FIRST TWO PLACES I WENT
WERE OUT OF CANTALOUPE, SO...

30:30.045 --> 30:31.525
FOR THE LOVE OF GOD,
I NEED A COFFEE.

30:31.612 --> 30:34.006
YOU'RE ON WATCH.
YOU GOT THIS?
YES, MA'AM.

30:34.093 --> 30:35.964
BEHAVE.

30:36.051 --> 30:39.098
OF COURSE, MEIN KOMMANDANT.

30:41.752 --> 30:43.058
IT'S TIME FOR MY NAP.

30:48.629 --> 30:51.110
[ WHALES SINGING]

30:56.245 --> 30:58.378
THE, UH, MATING CALL
OF THE BELUGA WHALE --

30:58.465 --> 31:01.207
HELPS PUT ME
INTO A DEEP R.E.M. SLEEP.

31:01.294 --> 31:03.644
THANKS FOR THE UPDATE.

31:30.323 --> 31:32.542
[ WHIRRING ]

31:47.209 --> 31:49.342
[ SINGING CONTINUES]

31:51.387 --> 31:52.693
HERE I COME, PETER.

31:52.780 --> 31:54.869
WISH ME LUCK, MELON ME.

32:05.314 --> 32:08.404
IT HAS BEEN A LONG TIME SINCE
I HAD A CLANDESTINE MEETING.

32:08.491 --> 32:11.190
HERE ARE THE THINGS
THAT YOU'VE ASKED FOR.

32:11.277 --> 32:13.540
YOU ARE A BEACON
IN A STORM, JUNE.

32:13.627 --> 32:16.108
YOU BET YOUR ASS.
HOW DID YOU ESCAPE?

32:16.195 --> 32:19.850
LET'S JUST SAY I USED MY HEAD --
WELL, A VERSION OF MY HEAD.

32:19.938 --> 32:22.462
I THINK I BOUGHT ENOUGH TIME
TO GET A JUMP START ON THEM.

32:22.549 --> 32:24.333
OKAY.
ALL RIGHT, YES.I'LL SEE YOU, DARLING.

32:24.420 --> 32:26.553
[ SINGING CONTINUES]

32:32.689 --> 32:34.430
Mozzie's voice: I'M STILL REPOSING, FED.

32:34.517 --> 32:36.084
HE EVEN SLEEPS ANNOYING.

32:40.262 --> 32:42.351
Announcer:
AND IT'S RAINCLOUD JIM
BY 3 1/2 LENGTHS,

32:42.438 --> 32:46.660
FOLLOWED BY MY EX-BEST FRIEND AND GOLDHOARDER'S FOLLY!

32:46.747 --> 32:48.357
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

32:48.444 --> 32:49.576
FOUR IN A ROW.

32:49.663 --> 32:51.839
MUST BE
THE LUCK OF THE IRISH.

32:51.926 --> 32:54.233
MUST BE. I THINK I'LL PUT
ANOTHER $5,000 DOWN.

32:56.713 --> 32:58.585
O'LEARY'S STILL BETTING
THE MINIMUM.

32:58.672 --> 33:00.413
CAN YOU BLAME THE GUY?
HE'S CAUTIOUS.

33:00.500 --> 33:03.111
MM. MM.

33:06.419 --> 33:07.768
[ SIGHS ]

33:07.855 --> 33:09.465
ONE RACE LEFT.

33:09.552 --> 33:12.773
IF O'LEARY DOESN'T BET BIG,
THE FBI's OUT 100 GRAND,

33:12.860 --> 33:14.253
DE LUCA WON'T BE HAPPY...

33:14.340 --> 33:15.950
AND MOZZIE
WILL NEVER BE SAFE.

33:16.037 --> 33:17.691
[ SIGHS ]

33:17.778 --> 33:19.649
I'LL TALK TO O'LEARY,
SEE IF I CAN --YOU'RE FIRED.

33:19.736 --> 33:21.651
WHAT?
PUBLICLY...

33:21.738 --> 33:23.436
BY ME, RIGHT NOW.

33:25.090 --> 33:26.874
LOOK, I-I DON'T KNOW

33:26.961 --> 33:29.137
WHO IS STEALING THE MONEY FROM
THE REGISTERS, BUT IT'S NOT ME.

33:29.224 --> 33:30.225
NO, IT IS YOU.
IT IS YOU!

33:30.312 --> 33:31.705
YOU KNOW WHAT?!

33:31.792 --> 33:34.403
COME HERE! OKAY?
HEY!

33:34.490 --> 33:37.232
YOU WERE TROUBLE EVER SINCE
YOU CAME TO WORK FOR ME

33:37.319 --> 33:40.888
WITH YOUR GLOSSY SMILE
AND THOSE ANNOYING LITTLE HATS.

33:40.975 --> 33:42.324
YOU LOVEMY HATS.

33:42.411 --> 33:43.543
THE HELL I DID!

33:43.630 --> 33:44.892
ALL RIGHT,
YOU'RE INSUBORDINATE,

33:44.979 --> 33:46.285
YOU NEVER DO
WHAT I TELL YOU TO DO,

33:46.372 --> 33:48.635
AND EVERY TIME
I TURN MY BACK,

33:48.722 --> 33:51.116
YOU'RE OFF DOING WHO-KNOWS-WHAT
WITH GOD-KNOWS-WHO!

33:54.032 --> 33:55.468
I'M SORRY, FOLKS.
I'M SORRY.

33:55.555 --> 33:57.209
YOU KNOW,
YOU UNGRATEFUL BASTARD.

33:57.296 --> 33:59.341
I HAVE HAD YOUR BACK
SINCE DAY ONE,

33:59.428 --> 34:01.300
AND ANYTIME
ANYTHING GOES WRONG,

34:01.387 --> 34:03.084
I'M THE FIRST PERSON
YOU BLAME!

34:03.171 --> 34:04.390
'CAUSE YOU'RE A CON!

34:04.477 --> 34:07.306
IT'S WHO YOU ARE,
AND IT'S ALL YOU'LL EVER BE.

34:07.393 --> 34:09.482
NO, NO, NO, NO.
HEY, HEY.

34:09.569 --> 34:11.527
YOU'RE FIRED!
GET OUT OF MY SIGHT!

34:11.614 --> 34:12.746
YOU KNOW WHAT?
WITH PLEASURE.
GOOD.

34:12.833 --> 34:14.835
AND THE NEXT TIME
YOUR HOT WIFE GETS LONELY...

34:16.184 --> 34:18.099
...TELL HER TO CALL ME.

34:18.186 --> 34:19.579
[ CROWD MURMURING ]

34:19.666 --> 34:21.146
YOU KNOW MY NUMBER.WHOA. WHOA, WHOA, WHOA.

34:21.233 --> 34:22.625
THAT'S IT?
YOU'RE JUST GONNA WALK OUT?

34:22.712 --> 34:24.845
WHAT THE HELL WAS THAT?WATCH.

34:24.932 --> 34:26.020
YOU HEARD THE GUY.
I'M DONE HERE.

34:26.107 --> 34:27.239
THERE'S ONE RACE LEFT.

34:27.326 --> 34:28.631
I CAN'T TAKE THIS GUY DOWN
WITHOUT YOU.

34:28.718 --> 34:31.112
YOU CAN'T TAKE THIS GUY DOWN
WITH A MINIMUM BET.

34:31.199 --> 34:32.766
ALL RIGHT, ALL RIGHT,
I'M ALL-IN.

34:32.853 --> 34:34.028
IT'S TOO LATE.

34:34.115 --> 34:36.509
I CUT YOU IN 30%.

34:36.596 --> 34:38.206
[ "FIRST CALL" PLAYS]

34:40.513 --> 34:42.515
ALL RIGHT.

34:42.602 --> 34:44.865
SARATOGA, NINTH RACE.

34:44.952 --> 34:46.649
$800,000 --
SOVEROW'S SHAME TO WIN.

34:46.736 --> 34:48.086
YES, SIR.

34:59.271 --> 35:01.403
[ SINGING CONTINUES]

35:01.490 --> 35:03.405
[ IMITATING
WHALES SINGING ]

35:03.492 --> 35:04.754
[ Rapping ]
♪ THUG LIFE♪

35:04.841 --> 35:06.626
♪ BITCH LIFE, HO LIFE♪

35:06.713 --> 35:08.410
♪ TELL ME NOW, WHICH ONE OF YOU LIVING A STRAIGHT LI--♪

35:08.497 --> 35:10.020
[ MUSIC STOPS ]

35:10.108 --> 35:11.935
Mozzie's voice: HEY, I'M SLEEPING IN HERE!

35:12.022 --> 35:13.720
♪ THUG LIFE♪

35:13.807 --> 35:15.330
♪ BITCH LIFE, HO LIFE♪

35:15.417 --> 35:17.724
Blake:
UM, AGENT BERRIGAN?

35:21.162 --> 35:22.598
DAMN IT, MOZZIE!

35:24.165 --> 35:25.688
[ CELL PHONE RINGS ]

35:29.301 --> 35:30.650
HEY, DIANA.
EVERYTHING OKAY?

35:30.737 --> 35:32.913
MOZZIE PULLED
A FERRIS BUELLER.
HE'S OUT?

35:33.000 --> 35:34.219
YEAH, THAT'S NOT
THE WORST OF IT.

35:37.091 --> 35:38.658
Announcer: SOVEROW'S SHAME IN THE LEAD,

35:38.745 --> 35:41.226
BUT COMING UP ON THE OUTSIDE IS AMAZON EDDIE!

35:41.313 --> 35:44.316
AMAZON EDDIE
MOVES INTO THE LEAD!

35:44.403 --> 35:46.666
NOW MIGHT BE A GOOD TIME
TO SLIP OUT.

35:46.753 --> 35:48.146
TELL DE LUCA I'M READY.

35:48.233 --> 35:50.235
NICE WORK.
HE'LL BE EXPECTING YOU.

35:50.322 --> 35:52.672
NOW TWO LENGTHS!

35:52.759 --> 35:54.282
SOVEROW'S SHAME TRYING HER BEST TO MAKE UP GROUND,

35:54.369 --> 35:55.762
BUT IT'S TOO LITTLE TOO LATE.

35:55.849 --> 35:56.719
IT'S AMAZON EDDIE FOR THE WIN!

35:56.806 --> 35:58.243
NO!

35:58.330 --> 36:00.332
I WAS SET UP.

36:00.419 --> 36:02.551
THIS WHOLE DAMN THING
WAS A SETUP.

36:02.638 --> 36:03.944
YOU DID THIS.
WHAT?

36:04.031 --> 36:05.467
HEY, IS THERE A PROBLEM?THERE'S A PROBLEM.

36:05.554 --> 36:07.687
HE HAD HIS GUY LURE ME HERE
TO GET MY MONEY WITH A DELAY.

36:07.774 --> 36:08.644
I DON'T KNOW
WHAT YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

36:08.731 --> 36:10.124
YOU'RE DAMN STRAIGHT
YOU DO.

36:10.211 --> 36:11.430
YOU KNOW WHO I AM,

36:11.517 --> 36:13.127
AND YOU KNOW
WHAT I'M CAPABLE OF, OKAY?

36:13.214 --> 36:14.607
SO YOU TELL
YOUR ASSOCIATE --

36:14.694 --> 36:17.653
MY ASSOCIATE IS A CON ARTIST,
WHICH IS WHY I FIRED HIM.

36:17.740 --> 36:20.003
SO LISTEN -- I DON'T WANT TO
CAUSE ANOTHER SCENE HERE.

36:20.090 --> 36:22.876
SO HOW ABOUT I JUST GIVE YOU
THE MONEY THAT YOU CAME IN WITH,

36:22.963 --> 36:24.878
YOU WALK OUT OF HERE,
AND WE'LL CALL IT EVEN?

36:33.756 --> 36:35.976
HEY. YOU GET O'LEARY
CALMED DOWN?

36:36.063 --> 36:37.412
HE WENT FOR IT.

36:37.499 --> 36:39.545
JONES IS ESCORTING HIM
AND HIS MONEY OUT BACK.

36:39.632 --> 36:40.807
THAT'S ONE PROBLEM DOWN.

36:40.894 --> 36:42.635
WE HAVE ANOTHER PROBLEM?
YEAH.

36:59.913 --> 37:01.741
I GOT YOUR TEXT.

37:01.828 --> 37:04.134
YOU'D BETTER HAVE A DAMN GOOD
REASON FOR CHANGING THE MEET.

37:04.222 --> 37:07.529
AS MY MONIKER SUGGESTS,
I'M A BIG FAN OF BRIDGEWORK.

37:07.616 --> 37:09.488
I DON'T HAVE TIME FOR GAMES.
GIVE ME O'LEARY'S MONEY.

37:13.318 --> 37:14.754
FRANK DE LUCA JR.

37:14.841 --> 37:16.234
WE MEET AGAIN.
LONG TIME, FRANKIE.

37:16.321 --> 37:17.626
WHO THE HELL ARE YOU?

37:17.713 --> 37:21.064
I'M THE MAN YOUR FATHER
SPENT 30 YEARS LOOKING FOR.

37:22.979 --> 37:25.199
I'M THE REAL
DENTIST OF DETROIT.

37:30.944 --> 37:32.598
[ TIRES SCREECH ]

37:32.685 --> 37:34.252
Jones: S.W.A.T.'s
STILL FIVE MINUTES AWAY.

37:34.339 --> 37:36.384
I WANT A PERIMETER
AROUND THE BRIDGE.

37:36.471 --> 37:38.386
WHAT THE HELL
WAS MOZZIE THINKING?

37:38.473 --> 37:40.780
NO CLUE.

37:40.867 --> 37:42.738
ALL RIGHT, SO THE GUY FROM THE
MEETING A COUPLE OF DAYS --

37:42.825 --> 37:43.913
WORKS FOR ME.

37:44.000 --> 37:45.959
I'M THE MAN
WHO SCAMMED YOUR FATHER.

37:46.046 --> 37:48.091
NO MYTH --
THE LEGEND OF DETROIT.GUYS, GUYS.

37:48.178 --> 37:50.311
IT ENDS HERE, TODAY,
ON THIS STREET.

37:50.398 --> 37:52.444
SERIOUSLY,
WHO THE HELL ARE YOU?

37:52.531 --> 37:53.967
1981, BRUSH PARK.

37:54.054 --> 37:56.796
YOU KNOCKED MY BUBBLE-GUM
ICE-CREAM CONE ONTO THE GROUND.

37:56.883 --> 37:59.277
REALLY?
THAT WAS YOU?

37:59.364 --> 38:01.279
YOUMADE A FOOL
OF MY FATHER?

38:01.366 --> 38:03.324
AND YOUR FATHER HAD A THING
FOR BLOOD FEUDS,

38:03.411 --> 38:05.413
AND HE ENDED UP SIX FEET UNDER
BECAUSE OF IT.

38:05.500 --> 38:07.502
YET HERE YOU ARE,
DOING THE EXACT SAME THING.

38:07.589 --> 38:09.287
I THOUGHT YOU WANTED TO BE
YOUR OWN MAN, JUNIOR.

38:10.766 --> 38:11.985
CAN'T MAKE OUT A WEAPON
ON DE LUCA.

38:12.072 --> 38:13.203
SHOULD WE MOVE IN?

38:13.291 --> 38:14.988
WE'VE GOT
NOTHING ON HIM

38:15.075 --> 38:17.207
UNLESS DE LUCA PICKS UP
THAT BRIEFCASE.

38:17.295 --> 38:19.340
THAT O'LEARY'S CASH?
YEAH.

38:19.427 --> 38:21.734
BUT WE BOTH KNOW
THIS ISN'T ABOUT THE MONEY.

38:21.821 --> 38:24.519
THIS IS ABOUT TAKING ME DOWN,
ONLY IT DIDN'T WORK.

38:24.606 --> 38:26.391
WELL, I CAN TAKE CARE
OF THAT RIGHT NOW.

38:26.478 --> 38:27.827
YEAH, YOU COULD.

38:27.914 --> 38:30.177
COME ON, MOZ.
GIVE IT TO HIM.

38:30.264 --> 38:32.179
AND THEN MY PEOPLE
COULD GO AFTER YOU,

38:32.266 --> 38:34.137
AND YOUR PEOPLE
COULD COME AFTER MINE.

38:34.224 --> 38:35.313
YOU SEE
WHERE THIS IS GOING?

38:36.966 --> 38:38.968
WHAT THE HELL
IS MOZZIE DOING?

38:39.055 --> 38:40.535
FIGHTING
HIS OWN WAR.

38:40.622 --> 38:41.710
WE CAN END THIS.

38:41.797 --> 38:43.364
YOU COULD JUST WALK AWAY,

38:43.451 --> 38:45.584
AND THE SUITS
CAN'T TOUCH YOU.

38:45.671 --> 38:47.325
WHAT DO YOU MEAN -- THE SUITS?
YOU TALKING ABOUT THE FEDS?

38:47.412 --> 38:50.937
YEAH. ONLY YOU KNOW THEM
AS MY LIP MAN AND HIS BOSS.

38:51.024 --> 38:52.330
YOU SET ME UP?

38:52.417 --> 38:55.245
YOU SET ME UP,
YOU FREAKIN' WEASEL?!

38:55.333 --> 38:57.944
AW, SOMEONE
GOT DOUBLE-CROSSED IN THIS?

38:58.031 --> 38:59.772
WE SHOULD ALL
BE SHOCKED.

38:59.859 --> 39:01.077
THAT'S WHAT HAPPENS.

39:01.164 --> 39:02.514
I'M GONNA TURN
AND WALK AWAY.

39:02.601 --> 39:04.472
YOU CAN BE SMART
AND DO THE SAME THING,

39:04.559 --> 39:06.431
OR YOU CAN MAKE THE SAME MISTAKE
YOUR FATHER DID.

39:07.910 --> 39:10.696
YOUR DECISION.

39:10.783 --> 39:12.915
PICK IT UP.
PICK IT UP.

39:18.051 --> 39:19.182
HEY!

39:19.269 --> 39:20.488
HEY!

39:23.273 --> 39:25.537
MY FATHER WOULD HAVE
WANTED IT THISWAY.

39:25.624 --> 39:27.190
FBI!
FBI!

39:27.277 --> 39:29.279
DROP YOUR WEAPON!DROP YOUR WEAPON!

39:29.367 --> 39:30.846
[ SIREN WAILS, TIRES SCREECH ]DROP YOUR WEAPON!

39:30.933 --> 39:33.545
FBI!
FBI!

39:33.632 --> 39:34.981
DROP IT, DROP IT!
DROP IT!
FREEZE!

39:35.068 --> 39:36.330
DROP YOUR WEAPON!

39:39.594 --> 39:41.291
[ GUN CLATTERS ]

39:41.379 --> 39:43.468
NOW I'VE GOT YOU ON EXTORTION
ANDATTEMPTED MURDER.

39:43.555 --> 39:45.208
YOU SHOULD HAVE
LISTENED TO HIM.

39:47.036 --> 39:48.342
HOPE IT WAS WORTH IT,
DE LUCA.

39:52.346 --> 39:54.217
PLEASE DON'T GO ROGUE
ON ME AGAIN.

39:54.304 --> 39:55.871
WHAT THE HELL
IS WRONG WITH YOU?

39:55.958 --> 39:57.699
YOU SHOULD HAVE LET ME
HANDLE THIS.

39:57.786 --> 40:00.789
DE LUCA'S ALWAYS ARMED,
AND HE'S GOOD.

40:00.876 --> 40:02.312
S.W.A.T. OR NOT,

40:02.400 --> 40:04.184
HE MOST LIKELY
WOULD HAVE SHOT YOU, SUIT.

40:04.271 --> 40:06.012
AND IF WE HADN'T
SHOWN UP?
I KNEW YOU WOULD.

40:08.188 --> 40:09.232
THANK YOU, PETER.

40:11.670 --> 40:15.195
YOU GUYS EVER TRIED
BUBBLE-GUM ICE CREAM?

40:21.723 --> 40:24.030
[ DOOR OPENS ]

40:24.117 --> 40:26.380
HEY...

40:26.467 --> 40:28.034
YOU GOT YOUR STUFF
FROM THE FEDS.

40:28.121 --> 40:30.079
YEAH, COMPLETE
WITH FBI TAINT.

40:32.081 --> 40:34.432
YOU DOING OKAY, MOZ?

40:34.519 --> 40:36.042
I KNOW HOW HARD IT IS
TO GIVE UP EVERYTHING.

40:36.129 --> 40:37.609
I-I COULDN'T DO IT.

40:37.696 --> 40:39.306
I KEPT A PART OF JEFFRIES
WITH ME,

40:39.393 --> 40:41.961
AND I KNOW I'M LUCKY
I GET TO DO THAT.

40:42.048 --> 40:45.181
AND I KNOW YOUR CONNECTION
TO THE FBI,

40:45.268 --> 40:47.314
BUT IT'S NOT WHO WE ARE.

40:47.401 --> 40:50.404
WHEN WE DO FINALLY
GET TO SELL OUR ART,

40:50.491 --> 40:52.014
WE REALLY HAVE TO
REMEMBER THAT.

40:52.101 --> 40:53.712
WHAT ARE YOU SAYING?

40:55.757 --> 40:59.718
OH, YOU AND PETER --

40:59.805 --> 41:01.981
ENJOY IT
WHILE IT LASTS.

41:02.068 --> 41:05.332
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

41:05.419 --> 41:08.335
HOPE YOU DON'T MIND --
I BROUGHT A FRIEND.

41:08.422 --> 41:10.337
MR. JEFFRIES?

41:10.424 --> 41:12.644
[ Laughing ]
YOU'RE OKAY!

41:12.731 --> 41:14.167
[ JEFFRIES CHUCKLES ]

41:14.254 --> 41:16.865
YOUR FBI FRIENDS FOUND ME
AT LADY LIBERTY.

41:16.952 --> 41:18.301
I'M GLAD YOU GOT
MY CLUES.

41:18.388 --> 41:21.609
I TOLD YOU, SUIT.

41:21.696 --> 41:23.176
YOU HAVEN'T CHANGED
AT ALL,

41:23.263 --> 41:25.134
EXCEPT FOR A BIT MORE CHARACTER
UP THERE.

41:25.221 --> 41:27.963
OH, WELL, FATHER TIME
HAS A CRUEL SENSE OF HUMOR.

41:28.050 --> 41:29.878
HOW'S EVERYTHING
DOWN AT THE GROUP HOME?

41:29.965 --> 41:31.358
I KNOW MY DONATIONS
WEREN'T MUCH, BUT...

41:31.445 --> 41:32.533
THEY WERE ENOUGH.

41:32.620 --> 41:33.969
THE SMALLEST GOOD DEED

41:34.056 --> 41:36.189
IS WORTH MORE
THAN THE GRANDEST INTENTION.

41:36.276 --> 41:37.538
OH, DUGUET.

41:37.625 --> 41:40.019
GOOD DEEDS ARE THE SEEDS
TO GOOD ACTIONS.

41:40.106 --> 41:42.761
[ LAUGHS ] TEMPLE.
"ACTION IS ELOQUENCE."

41:42.848 --> 41:44.240
SHAKESPEARE.

41:44.327 --> 41:46.634
"FALSE ELOQUENCE
IS EXAGGERATION --

41:46.721 --> 41:48.810
TRUE ELOQUENCE
IS EMPHASIS."

41:48.897 --> 41:50.769
[ LAUGHS ] ALGER.
GOOD ONE.

41:50.856 --> 41:52.640
ARE THEY REALLY HAVING
A QUOTE-OFF?
OH, YEAH.

41:52.727 --> 41:54.903
MY GOODNESS.

41:54.990 --> 41:56.557
IS THAT MOZART?
[ CHUCKLES ]

41:56.644 --> 41:58.211
OH.

41:58.298 --> 41:59.560
HE LOVED
THIS LITTLE BEAR --

41:59.647 --> 42:01.127
COULDN'T PRONOUNCE
HIS NAME, THOUGH.

42:01.214 --> 42:02.868
KEPT CALLING IT
"MOZZIE."

42:09.222 --> 42:10.353
[ CHUCKLES ]

42:10.440 --> 42:12.007
A SENTIMENTALIST.

42:12.094 --> 42:13.487
YEAH.

42:13.574 --> 42:14.967
I CAN'T BELIEVE MOZZIE

42:15.054 --> 42:17.360
KEPT TABS ON JEFFRIES
ALL THESE YEARS.

42:17.447 --> 42:19.537
SOMETIMES
IT'S HARD TO SAY GOOD-BYE.

42:19.624 --> 42:21.451
MM.
